OL,3,CWater returns to villages after a
OL,4,Cweekend of outages in record hot May
OL,6,FResidents of three villages in Kent
OL,7,Fhave now had their water supplies
OL,8,Freturned after three days of outages
OL,9,Fin scorching temperatures.
OL,11,FSupply issues in Charing, Challock and
OL,12,FMolash were first reported at around
OL,13,F8:30am on Saturday morning and
OL,14,Faffected customers are still warned to
OL,15,Fexpect lower pressure on Tuesday, 26
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FSouth East Water (SEW) has apologised
OL,19,Ffor the problems, which it said
OL,20,Ffollowed a technical failure at its
OL,21,Fpumping station near Charing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
