PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779894668
OL,3,CWater returns to villages after a
OL,4,Cweekend of outages in record hot May
OL,6,FA bottled water station was set up
OL,7,Fover the long weekend for affected
OL,8,Fresidents and reopened today for
OL,9,Fanyone that needs it.
OL,11,FIt comes as the UK experienced its
OL,12,Fhottest May day of all time on Monday
OL,13,Fwhen Kew Gardens in south-west London
OL,14,Fhit 34.8C.
OL,16,FIn East Sussex, Herstmonceux was the
OL,17,Fhottest spot, reaching 31.5C, while in
OL,18,FKent, Frittenden saw a high of 30.5C
OL,19,Fon Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
