OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779894668
OL,3,CWater returns to villages after a
OL,4,Cweekend of outages in record hot May
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn a statement on Tuesday morning,
OL,12,FSouth East Water said: "Customers
OL,13,Fshould now have their water returned
OL,14,Fthis morning albeit at lower pressure.
OL,16,F"We are sorry for the lack of the
OL,17,Fsupply over the bank holiday weekend.
OL,18,FExceptionally high temperatures has,
OL,19,Fas expected, created very high demand
OL,20,Ffor tap water supplies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779894668
OL,3,CWater returns to villages after a
OL,4,Cweekend of outages in record hot May
OL,6,F"We had planned for very high demand
OL,7,Fgiven the weather forecasts by
OL,8,Fincreasing output at our water
OL,9,Ftreatment works across our supply area
OL,10,Fand putting extra water into the
OL,11,Fnetwork.
OL,13,F"Our fleet of tankers has been working
OL,14,F24/7 putting additional water into the
OL,15,Fnetwork in areas where demand has been
OL,16,Fextremely high and to support our
OL,17,Fstored water reservoirs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779894668
OL,3,CWater returns to villages after a
OL,4,Cweekend of outages in record hot May
OL,6,F"However, due to the nature of water
OL,7,Fsupply networks, some customers on
OL,8,Fhigher ground or at the far end of the
OL,9,Fnetwork may have had low pressure or
OL,10,Fsupply interruptions, especially at
OL,11,Fpeak use times.
OL,13,F"A bottle station is open Challock
OL,14,FVillage Hall Blind Lane, Challock,
OL,15,FAshford TN25 4AU for anyone that needs
OL,16,Fit.
OL,18,F"Once again, we're really sorry about
OL,19,Fthe disruption."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
